description:
Mô Tả Công Việc


              - Work directly with Technical Director (Japanese) to assist him in daily operational tasks, especially translation;

              - Be interpreter in meetings, conferences, customer meetings;

              - Translate documents, technical documents of the Company;

              - Compose documents, reports in Japanese, or English (if any);

              - Support and join events introducing the capacity and experience of the Company with domestic and foreign partners;

              - Other tasks assigned by the Technical Director.


              Xem toàn bộ Mô Tả Công Việc

requirement:
Yêu Cầu Công Việc


              - Japanese N2 Certificate;

              - University degree with major in Engineering/Construction is a plus;

              - Have experience in Japanese companies is an advantage;

              - Proficiency in office computer;

              - 03 years of experience working in translation or interpretation in Japanese;

              - Be able to communicate in English;

              - Hard working and high responsibility;


              (JapanWorks)

              n02level, n01level, WorkWithJapanese, 170412, 170413, 170414


              Xem toàn bộ Yêu Cầu Công Việc
